{"tid":1697416,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喇沙書院白色恐怖","createTime":"2019-11-07T00:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T15:12:05.000Z","uid":337655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"15fc5972fcb6ebe877c52f9809470984eedc4352","tid":1697416,"uid":337655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T00:19:09.000Z","msg":"#repost @lsc_antielab_<br />\n・・・<br />\n於6/11陸運會完結後, 有約70名學生自發走出跑道高叫口號並合唱《願榮光歸香港》, 部分學生穿著黑衣並蒙面, 亦有學生揮動「光復香港」旗幟.<br />\n<br />\n活動完結後, 訓導主任麥老師無理紀錄身穿黑衣同學的名字。由於放學後身穿黑衣沒有違反任何一條校規, 而陸運會期間亦無明確服裝指示予運動員。故此學生要求麥老師解釋紀錄下同學名字的原因，但麥老師拒絕回應, 亦有某位藝術科老師甚至用數碼相機對學生進行拍攝。<br />\n以上的行為使學生感到恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n唐校長與其他老師對事件未有深刻了解, 而處理這件事情的麥老師卻站在後方一言不發, 並且態度惡劣, 使學生感到極度不滿。<br />\n<br />\n事發幾個小時後校方指出需要花更多時間了解事情, 要在下星期一才能回應學生, 關注組與其他學生都認為這是無理拖延。<br />\n<br />\n關注組首先為部分學生對校方態度較激動道歉, 但同時亦希望校方能理解學生態度偏激的原因, 是基於麥老師對學生的不尊重及處理手法欠缺透明度。關注組及一眾學生都盼望能夠與校方互相尊重, 理解並釋除一切誤會。<br />\n<br />\n以下是對校方的請求：<br />\n1）請讓同學和校方進行對話（尤其是麥老師）<br />\n2）請麥老師解釋紀錄黑衣同學名字的原因。<br />\n3）請解釋為什麼有老師對抗議的學生們進行拍攝<br />\n<br />\n如果星期一校方沒有回應以上的訴求，學生們不排除有進一步的行動。<br />\n<br />\nBoys of courage, boys of daring.🔴⚪<br />\n#lasallecollege <br />\n#喇沙書院反修例關注組 <br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可 <br />\n#光復香港時代革命 <br />\n#香港人反抗 <br />\n#standwithhongkong"},{"pid":"c2b03a0695c86f03823b5095724995b8362ae97c","tid":1697416,"uid":235875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T00:21:15.000Z","msg":"教畜張相呢，全部嘢放上黎"},{"pid":"01911a6bd7276686784611a790223607450dbec6","tid":1697416,"uid":4172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T00:24:39.000Z","msg":"香港人 反抗"},{"pid":"ba00bb3dd5964c4af52a52eeea2381bed85a7b4d","tid":1697416,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T00:24:51.000Z","msg":"驚閪"},{"pid":"a34e93ac3f57de3aca2e4d56dfaff574a6ed46f9","tid":1697416,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T00:25:07.000Z","msg":"[重新整合]11.10 7區開花！ 11.11全港3罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7571faa52ff19e7dd19119d4414ae9616d3138d7","tid":1697416,"uid":276319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T00:27:51.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"bd04862b4e19a2a72a7909d0c728e8ead3bab4bb","tid":1697416,"uid":337655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T00:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S8G8KFL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS8G8KFL.jpg&h=301cc182&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8abca74ac7c08be051af10dfc51f80e03152967e","tid":1697416,"uid":299825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:09:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e453888933ab5399157efa3e96bad7f52d7a7129","tid":1697416,"uid":10207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:13:02.000Z","msg":"John mak?"},{"pid":"062a74953c927309301c39c63e798455c1885ac1","tid":1697416,"uid":337655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e453888933ab5399157efa3e96bad7f52d7a7129","tid":1697416,"uid":10207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:13:02.000Z","msg":"John mak?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:52:06.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"94996d9ed21e73a9a61a4a56092d6324eb615732","tid":1697416,"uid":10207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"062a74953c927309301c39c63e798455c1885ac1","tid":1697416,"uid":337655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e453888933ab5399157efa3e96bad7f52d7a7129","tid":1697416,"uid":10207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:13:02.000Z","msg":"John mak?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:52:06.000Z","msg":"Yes"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"he is always on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}